import Vue from 'vue'
import Offset from '@/components/helper/Offset'
import Card from '@/components/material/Card'
import LineChartCard from '@/components/material/LineChartCard'
import PieChartCard from '@/components/material/PieChartCard'
import Notification from '@/components/material/Notification'
import StatsCard from '@/components/material/StatsCard'

Vue.component(Offset.name, Offset)
Vue.component(Card.name, Card)
Vue.component(LineChartCard.name, LineChartCard)
Vue.component(PieChartCard.name, PieChartCard)
Vue.component(Notification.name, Notification)
Vue.component(StatsCard.name, StatsCard)
